# Test: hub started without ze.web.ui (Phases 1-3 default) renders Finder
# VALIDATES: AC-1a (Finder is default; V2 workbench markers absent)
# PREVENTS: Workbench markers leaking into the rollback path
#
# Spec: plan/spec-web-2-operator-workbench.md (UI Mode Contract).
# Notes: This test depends on the hub being started without
# `ze.web.ui=workbench`. The default ze-test web invocation satisfies that.

option=timeout:value=30s

action=open:path=/show/
expect=element:not-text=panic
expect=element:not-text=workbench
